flowchart TD
    A["User Input:<br/>- Favorite Genre<br/>- Favorite Mood<br/>- Target Energy"] --> B[Load Songs from songs.csv]
    B --> C{For each Song}
    C --> D["Check Genre Match<br/>+2.0 if match"]
    C --> E["Check Mood Match<br/>+1.0 if match"]
    C --> F["Calculate Energy Similarity<br/>score = 1 - |song_energy - user_energy|"]
    D & E & F --> G["Sum Weighted Score<br/>score = genre + mood + energy"]
    G --> H[Store Song and Score]
    H --> I{All Songs Scored?}
    I -- No --> C
    I -- Yes --> J[Sort Songs by Score Descending]
    J --> K[Select Top K Songs]
    K --> L["Output:<br/>Top K Recommendations<br/>[Title, Artist, Score, Explanation]"]